{"tid":173070,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣「男友視角」畫面流出　躺床甜喊晚安萌翻","createTime":"2017-03-26T05:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T15:39:23.000Z","uid":9573,"like":62,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"55ad23c7f4f7fd9be27e26a3d36150b1ff27d1fe","tid":173070,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T05:44:01.000Z","msg":"日本女星新垣結衣日前演出夯劇《月薪嬌妻》，以甜美清純形象再度征服觀眾，人氣水漲船高，廣告活動邀約不斷。在近期推出的新廣告中，她獨自展開為期一天的旅行，並拿著自拍棒記綠全程，呈現出另類的「男友視角」，超萌畫面一出立刻引發熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2416/d2416525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2416%2Fd2416525.jpg&h=0da91237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲新垣結衣前陣子演出《月薪嬌妻》人氣暴增。<br />\n<br />\n新垣結衣近期替日本證券商「GMOクリック証券」拍攝的廣告中，以「Life is Going on」為主題，展開為期一日的小旅行，並手持自拍棒，將睡醒一直到睡前的旅途過程記錄下來。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2416/d2416522.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2416%2Fd2416522.jpg&h=076c1b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼新垣結衣自拍記綠一整天的旅行。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2416/d2416521.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2416%2Fd2416521.jpg&h=89e31ccd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n過程中，新垣結衣頻頻對著鏡頭，露出甜美微笑，不時自言自語、感性流淚，睡前也不忘對自拍畫面說了聲晚安，呈現出自己私底下最真實的一面，被認為是另類的「男友視角」，廣告一出立刻萌翻網友，在網路上掀起熱烈討論。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oMv8s0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoMv8s0e.jpg&h=87cca009&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼新垣結衣新廣告呈現出另類的「男友視角」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uc10B6G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUc10B6G.jpg&h=06f533fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n▼新垣結衣新廣告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e1HSF7Ml-hs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%